Name:           geekcode
Version:        1.7.3
Release:        alt2_11
Summary:        Geek Code generator
Summary(pl):    Generator Geek Code
Group:          Games/Other
License:        GPLv2+
URL:            http://sourceforge.net/projects/%{name}/
Source0:        http://downloads.sourceforge.net/%{name}/%{name}-%{version}.tar.gz
